tissues healthy over time,

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:03.300
and continue to make progress.

00:07:03.300 --> 00:07:05.300
If you don't want to do
that week off, don't do it.

00:07:05.300 --> 00:07:06.250
None of this is holy.

00:07:06.250 --> 00:07:07.930
