00:07:07.930 --> 00:07:09.960
Just ask yourself, what
are you going to emphasize

00:07:09.960 --> 00:07:12.050
and emphasize that, in
terms of the total volume

00:07:12.050 --> 00:07:14.920
of workouts that you do,
and work up incrementally,

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:17.360
and then move into another cycle.

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:18.630
That's what I suggest.

