And indeed, vision involves eyesight,

00:10:48.150 --> 00:10:50.800
our ability to see shapes,
and objects, and faces,

00:10:50.800 --> 00:10:52.480
and colors, and so forth.

00:10:52.480 --> 00:10:57.480
However, our eyes are responsible
for much more than that,

00:10:57.850 --> 00:11:01.320
including our mood,
our level of alertness,

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:05.330
and all of that is included
in what we call vision.

00:11:05.330 --> 00:11:08.910
So I just want to take about
three, maybe four minutes,

00:11:08.910 --> 00:11:12.790
and talk about how the visual
system works, how it's built,

00:11:12.790 --> 00:11:17.560
and how you are able to
so-called see things around you.

00:11:17.560 --> 00:11:19.670
I also want to describe the ways

