00:38:31.350 --> 00:38:33.570
I don't want to get into a
long description of this now,

00:38:33.570 --> 00:38:37.130
but basically the lens has
bring light to the retina,

00:38:37.130 --> 00:38:39.530
not in front of it, not behind it.

00:38:39.530 --> 00:38:43.270
If it brings light to a
position in front of the retina,

00:38:43.270 --> 00:38:47.050
then you won't see clearly, you
