00:40:25.270 --> 00:40:30.170
These melanopsin cells and
their activation by sunlight,

00:40:30.170 --> 00:40:33.543
completely subconsciously,
unaware, you're unaware of this,

00:40:34.400 --> 00:40:38.210
promote the health of
this system within the eye

00:40:38.210 --> 00:40:43.030
and allow you to offset the
myopia, nearsightedness.

00:40:43.030 --> 00:40:46.240
In other words, getting
outside for two hours a day,

00:40:46.240 --> 00:40:49.590
each day, on average, even
if there's cloud cover,

00:40:49.590 --> 00:40:51.600
without sunglasses on,

00:40:51.600 --> 00:40:56.600
will allow you to offset
the formation of myopia.

00:40:56.720 --> 00:40:58.520
Now, you might still form myopia

00:40:58.520 --> 00:41:00.220
if you have certain structural features

00:41:00.220 --> 00:41:01.370
or a genetic basis for that,

00:41:01.370 --> 00:41:03.590
we will talk about things
that you can do as well.

00:41:03.590 --> 00:41:05.840
But for everybody, we
should be doing this.

