00:43:31.710 --> 00:43:35.740
that we have these apparati
built into our eyes.

00:43:35.740 --> 00:43:37.430
So, we have lenses in our eyes,

00:43:37.430 --> 00:43:39.330
and we have these things
called the irises.

00:43:39.330 --> 00:43:41.020
You know, you're all
familiar with the iris,

00:43:41.020 --> 00:43:44.120
because you'll see people's
