when you come into this world are eyes.

00:44:01.990 --> 00:44:04.570
And actually, if you put the
little dots close together,

00:44:04.570 --> 00:44:06.810
it'll look kind of wrong,
like it's cross-eyed.

00:44:06.810 --> 00:44:09.200
And if you put them at different locations

00:44:09.200 --> 00:44:11.080
within those two dots,
of opposing locations,

00:44:11.080 --> 00:44:12.140
it'll look google-eyed.

00:44:12.140 --> 00:44:13.650
And so, your brain is actually filling in

00:44:13.650 --> 00:44:15.070
all the face and other information,

00:44:15.070 --> 00:44:16.850
even emotional information,

00:44:16.850 --> 00:44:19.390
just based on this recognition of eyes.

00:44:19.390 --> 00:44:21.660
And so, there's clearly we know this,

00:44:21.660 --> 00:44:22.517
there's real estate deep up in,

00:44:22.517 --> 00:44:24.750
you know, further up in the brain,

00:44:24.750 --> 00:44:29.380
that's responsible for
analyzing and recognizing faces

00:44:29.380 --> 00:44:30.750
and the eyes and the position

00:44:30.750 --> 00:44:32.520
of these little things we call irises,

00:44:32.520 --> 00:44:35.310
