00:45:16.150 --> 00:45:18.110
There's a connection
deep in the brainstem,

00:45:18.110 --> 00:45:20.510
deep back here in the brain near my neck,

00:45:20.510 --> 00:45:24.040
that connects the pupil
mechanism for the two eyes,

00:45:24.040 --> 00:45:25.090
and they're looking at the other eye.

00:45:25.090 --> 00:45:26.920
And if you shine light in one eye,

00:45:26.920 --> 00:45:29.160
and that people constricts
